{"tid":1825354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有手足整左條好高質既片--光復的前奏：反送中運動與香港人覺醒的軌跡","createTime":"2020-01-15T08:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T20:42:21.000Z","uid":116568,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"1c778eac36eb96c3cff67277fc9d3d07fa6dfd00","tid":1825354,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:08:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q3WdLkJS2yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dq3WdLkJS2yg&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=e68a4453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q3WdLkJS2yg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從無奇蹟天降的「英雄」，只有覺醒挺身的「凡人」。2019年，香港人的覺醒，讓數以百萬計的凡人挺身，在絕望中守護了香港的自由與尊嚴。這場運動所以能撼動世界，正因為反抗極權的意志皆出於人所共有的良知。<br />\n<br />\n這時序片回溯反送中運動的源起，回顧香港人逐步覺醒的軌跡，而整場運動雖然仍在發展，但香港人全面覺醒的分水嶺，就在佔領立法會、宣讀五大訴求的７月１日。<br />\n<br />\n如果「光復香港」的革命將是一部偉大史詩，反送中運動就是當中的前奏序章。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LTUkcxi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLTUkcxi.jpg&h=9ee3d6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2020 香港人 抗爭到底<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n119 遮打見</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e8aeb41b805b343e3373d696211b95d64444f75f","tid":1825354,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:09:19.000Z","msg":"119"},{"pid":"51d381b4a8a88d15f18ee1cc0f2d9b4cc2ad5164","tid":1825354,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:09:59.000Z","msg":"行動post推"},{"pid":"d0d836d4a3c46164140b7ef39f8237bbeeb370fa","tid":1825354,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51d381b4a8a88d15f18ee1cc0f2d9b4cc2ad5164","tid":1825354,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:09:59.000Z","msg":"行動post推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:10:34.000Z","msg"